OL,3,CNail polish, beards and haircuts: US
OL,4,CAir Force update appearance standards
OL,6,FThe US Air Force has updated its
OL,7,Fstandards around dress and appearance
OL,8,Fto include stricter rules around nail
OL,9,Fpolish, beards and haircuts.
OL,11,FThe newly implemented changes require
OL,12,Fwomen to only wear nail polish that is
OL,13,Fclear, or is a French or American
OL,14,Fmanicure.
OL,16,FIn a French manicure, the nail is
OL,17,Fpainted pale pink with a white tip. An
OL,18,FAmerican manicure is similar to this,
OL,19,Fbut uses a nude or pink base with a
OL,20,Fcream coloured tip.
