OL,3,CNail polish, beards and haircuts: US
OL,4,CAir Force update appearance standards
OL,6,FPreviously, a chart displayed a wide
OL,7,Frange of authorised colours that could
OL,8,Fbe worn by personnel.
OL,10,FThe compulsory guidance also clarifies
OL,11,Fthat male airmen "must be clean-shaven
OL,12,Fat the start of the duty day unless
OL,13,Fthey have a current medical profile or
OL,14,Freligious accommodation".
OL,16,FIt also clarifies that male hair must
OL,17,Fnot touch the ears.
OL,19,F"Hair will not touch the ears or
OL,20,Fprotrude under the front band of
OL,21,Fheadgear," the guidance states.
