OL,3,CNail polish, beards and haircuts: US
OL,4,CAir Force update appearance standards
OL,6,FPrevious guidance on hair, such as the
OL,7,Ftapered appearance of hair and the
OL,8,Fbulk of the hair not exceeding two and
OL,9,Fa half inches, remained the same.
OL,11,FIt also added the definition of a "gig
OL,12,Fline", which is where the front edge
OL,13,Fof the shirt, the belt buckle and the
OL,14,Ftrouser fly align.
OL,16,FAirmen are required to ensure this is
OL,17,F"straight and neat".
