OL,3,CNail polish, beards and haircuts: US
OL,4,CAir Force update appearance standards
OL,6,FIn a video released in December,
OL,7,FGeneral David W. Allvin, Air Force
OL,8,FChief of Staff, explained the reasons
OL,9,Fbehind the changes to standards.
OL,11,FHe said previous updates to guidance
OL,12,Fhad become more complex, leading to
OL,13,F"selective enforcement".
OL,15,FIn turn, he said this can "lead to
OL,16,Fsituations where the airmen believe
OL,17,Fthat they have the opportunity to do
OL,18,Fselective compliance."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
