OL,3,CNail polish, beards and haircuts: US
OL,4,CAir Force update appearance standards
OL,6,F"This is where the danger lies,
OL,7,Fbecause as airmen decide for
OL,8,Fthemselves whether they should comply
OL,9,Fwith the tech order or safety
OL,10,Fregulations or other instructions,
OL,11,Fthey may make the wrong choice, that's
OL,12,Funinformed," he continued.
OL,14,F"And the damage is to property,
OL,15,Fequipment or most importantly, we get
OL,16,Fairmen injured or killed.
OL,18,F"That's what's at stake, and that's
OL,19,Fwhat's driving some of these
OL,20,Fdecisions."
