OL,3,CNail polish, beards and haircuts: US
OL,4,CAir Force update appearance standards
OL,6,FThe document also stated that "pride"
OL,7,Fin an airman's uniform and appearance
OL,8,Fenhances "discipline".
OL,10,F"Pride in an Airman's personal
OL,11,Fappearance and uniform wear greatly
OL,12,Fenhances the discipline essential to
OL,13,Fan effective military force," it says.
OL,15,F"Therefore, Airmen must maintain a
OL,16,Fhigh standard of dress and personal
OL,17,Fappearance through adherence to the
OL,18,Ffive elements of this standard:
OL,19,Fneatness, cleanliness, safety,
OL,20,Funiformity, and military image."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
