OL,3,CNail polish, beards and haircuts: US
OL,4,CAir Force update appearance standards
OL,6,FIt added: "The image of a disciplined
OL,7,Fand committed Airman instils public
OL,8,Fconfidence that Airmen live by a
OL,9,Fcommon standard and respond to
OL,10,Fmilitary order and discipline."
OL,12,FSome members of the Air Force have
OL,13,Freacted to the changes online.
OL,15,FIn a video on TikTok, Elora Jean said
OL,16,F"people are not happy" with the new
OL,17,Fguidance.
