OL,6,F"They think the priorities are a
OL,7,Flittle bit skewed right now and nail
OL,8,Fpolish is not really that serious,"
OL,9,FJones said.
OL,11,F"There's a lot of other things that
OL,12,Fshould be focussed on when it comes to
OL,13,Fmilitary readiness and recruiting, and
OL,14,Fgeneral wellbeing."
